name: FiveO'ClockSomewhere
0:
”Alexa open five o'clock somewhere”
”Is it five o'clock?”
”Where is it five o'clock?”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: five o'clock somewhere
des: Five O'Clock Somewhere scours the globe to find places where it is already five o'clock. Alexa will also check the time at your location and congratulate you if you are lucky enough to be past five o'clock.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
